# NIX WHY-DEPENDS
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Show why a store path depends on another.
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix why-depends nixpkgs#hello nixpkgs#glibc: Show dependency chain.

### Essentials
- nix why-depends .#my-app nixpkgs#openssl: Investigate why your app needs openssl.

## Tips
- Great for reducing closure size by identifying unnecessary dependencies.

